# Phase2_Land Microsite — Build Brief

## Project Overview

This is a **showcase microsite** for Phase2_Land, a code- and AI-driven solution that converts deed documentation into a structured database and automatically generates a geodatabase for use in GIS applications.

The microsite serves as a **digital leave-behind and trade show booth display** for the AASHTO ROW conference in Cincinnati (end of April). It will run on a screen in the booth on autoplay, but must support manual navigation when someone walks up and engages. It is not the live app demo — that runs separately. This is the eye-catching overview.

