## Autoplay System

The autoplay toggle in the bottom nav controls a global autoplay state.

**When ON:**
- Hero beats advance automatically on a timer (each beat ~3-4 seconds, drawing animation plays at its own pace)
- Feature videos play through sequentially
- Advances to next section automatically
- Loops back to beginning after Info section
- Designed to run unattended on a trade show booth screen

**When OFF:**
- User controls everything via scroll and clicking feature items
- No automatic advancement

**Manual override:** If the user scrolls or clicks while autoplay is on, autoplay pauses. After 30 seconds of inactivity, autoplay resumes.

