## Technical Notes

- Match the tech stack of the prototype in `../prototype`
- Pull design tokens (colors, fonts, spacing, border radius) from prototype — do not hardcode values
- SVG polygon animation: use `stroke-dashoffset` technique
- Scroll-driven animations: use Intersection Observer or scroll-linked animation library consistent with prototype stack
- Videos: use `<video>` with `autoplay muted loop playsInline` attributes for demo clips
- Bottom nav active state: update based on scroll position using Intersection Observer
- Smooth scroll behavior throughout
- Optimized for a widescreen display (trade show monitor) — design at 1920x1080 as primary target, but should also work at standard laptop resolutions for post-conference use

